com.authlete.cbor

Class CBORDouble

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.authlete.cbor.CBORItem
      • com.authlete.cbor.CBORValue<TValue>
        • com.authlete.cbor.CBORNumber<Double>
          • com.authlete.cbor.CBORDouble

  • public class CBORDouble
extends CBORNumber<Double>
    CBOR double-precision floating-point number (major type = 7, additional information = 27).

    The CBORValue.getValue() method of this class returns an instance of Double.

    See Also:
    RFC 8949, 3.3. Floating-Point Numbers and Values with No Content
